## Build sessions

Each section below is **one Claude Code session**. Confirm or strike bullets before starting each.

### Session 1 — Fork & flag the backend
- Create a **new CI Supabase project** (its own project + env vars; staging-first; never touch the Astro-Psyche Lab project)
- Deploy the forked custom admin for CI; verify login + saving a draft article
- Add a **feature-flag config** — code-managed booleans, **Lewis-only** (Marie never sees a flag UI)
- **Flag OFF** the inherited non-MVP features: service price management, content-generation tools

### Session 2 — Magazine content model
- Extend the basic article upload to: the **9 categories**, **tags**, **author/byline**, **subtitle/deck**, **featured image**, **reading time**, **related-articles**
- Update the admin so Marie can set these fields when posting
- Migrations **staging-first**; seed the 9 categories; create author record(s)

### Session 3 — Public site & reading experience
- Build CI's Astro front-end from the prototype tokens/components (**CI's own brand**, not Gabriela's design): Home, Article template, Category pages, About, **"Únete"** landing, Contact, empty legal-page scaffolding
- Wire pages to pull content from the forked backend
- Reading experience as prototyped (byline, featured image, tags, related, share)
- Baseline: responsive, SEO basics, performance, accessibility
- Deploy to the **Vercel subdomain**

### Session 4 — Capture system + contact
- **Email signup via MailerLite** (reuse integration; CI's own audience), **double opt-in**, at footer / end-of-article / signup block / Únete page
- **Secondary channel CTA** — a channel-agnostic component (WhatsApp Channel | Telegram), swapped in once decided
- **Lead-magnet delivery** on signup (plumbing now, asset later)
- **Contact-form delivery** (decide where the message lands)

### Session 5 — Measurement, consent, legal & launch
*(Fullest session — may split if it runs long.)*
- Cookieless analytics (Plausible/Umami) + events: signup, channel click, article read, scroll depth, CTA clicks
- **Meta Pixel** (+ Conversions API optional), **consent-gated**
- **Consent banner / CMP** wired to consent mode (Pixel cannot fire pre-consent — EU)
- **UTM convention** + a cheat-sheet for Marie's social links
- Legal content: privacy, cookies, terms
- Final SEO (sitemap, structured data) + perf/a11y pass
- **Ship the MVP live** (`vercel.app`)

