## Definition of done (MVP)
- Site live on `vercel.app`
- Marie can publish a fully-formed article (with category, tags, image, byline) from the admin
- Email signup with **double opt-in** works end-to-end; lead magnet delivered
- Secondary channel CTA live
- Analytics + Meta Pixel + consent banner firing correctly (Pixel only after consent)
- Legal pages present
- Inherited features remain hidden behind flags

## Validation gate (decides whether v2 is earned)
Once live: **do Marie's social posts drive visits, and do those visitors convert to subscribers?** If yes → v2. If no → fix the funnel before building anything heavier.
